data.description: Cul-de-sac living in the sought-after Windmill Farms Addition! Located in the Choctaw/Nicoma Park school district, this beautiful custom built home is a true 4 bedroom home on an over-sized lot. The ceramic wood-grained tiles throughout the open-concept living/kitchen/dining area provide luxury and functionality. All four bedrooms provide plenty of floor space and come equipped with wood blinds. Master bathroom has a large soaker tub, separate shower, double sinks, and plenty of storage. Feel safe during the Oklahoma weather in your storm shelter, located in the garage, which also has epoxy flooring and insulated garage doors. Additional features to this home include sprinkler system, R35 insulation, Nest thermometer, night light plugs, USB plugs in Master, Cat 5 wiring, under cabinet lighting, along with gas and TV hook-ups outside. The neighborhood also offers a delightful playground and a pond, adding to the community's charm. This home's location is exceptionally convenient, situated in close proximity to I-40, Tinker Air Force Base, Choctaw and a plethora of excellent shops and restaurants.
